*** ChanServ Help - Command: SET AUTOHALFOP ***
Turns the Auto HalfOp option ON or OFF. When it is ON, ChanServ
will give HalfOp status to everyone who joins the channel.
 
Note: No changes will be made to the HOP list by this option.
 
Syntax:
/cs SET #channel AUTOHALFOP <ON|OFF>
 
Examples:
/cs SET #IRCHelp AUTOHALFOP OFF
/cs SET #debian AUTOHALFOP ON
 
Type /join #IRCHelp for more information.
*** End of Help ***
